The **Digital Archiving Portal **service allows to search documents which have been uploaded to Digital Archiving Stores through their metadata. It acts as a front-end portal to [Digital Archiving Store](/doxee-platform/docs/digital-archiving-stores-user-guide-doxee-platform-digital-archiving-stores-user-manual) resources which have been configured for this use.

Business users can conduct metadata searches either manually or by uploading a CSV file containing the search parameters. Furthermore, they can share the search results in various formats, as well as download the contents of archived documents.

## Key capabilities
Digital Archive is capable of safely storing any file format. Here are its main capabilities:

- **Customizable web portal:** Allows administrators to freely configure document metadata and search parameters using indexes and logical operators

- **CRM enhancement:** Facilitates tasks like document archiving and customer support

- **System integration:** Connects with existing CCM workflows, enabling the automatic archiving of generated communications

- **Access control:** Ensures security of stored data through dedicated authentication keys
